{"view":"article","slug":"skewb-skewb-lbl","category":"Skewb","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Skewb","title":{"en":"Skewb LBL Method"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Skewb LBL Method</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>FL</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>LL Corners</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>LL Center</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Side Centers</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>S = R' F R F', H = F R' F' R.</p><p><strong>FL (First Layer)</strong></p><p><strong>DBL Corner</strong></p><p>Solve D layer intuitively. Define an arrow as the adjacent center and corner with same color. Choose a face with an arrow as the face of the first layer, and treat the corner of arrow as solved corner, then put it on DBL. If there is no such face, convert it into previous case by a single move. </p><p><strong>DFL, DBR Corners</strong></p><p>Move some unsolved white corner (denoted by purple) to UFR using a single move.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"F' / f\">F' / f</span></p></td><td><p><strong>F</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>f</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UFR to DFL</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x U</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x z R' F\">x z R' F</span></p></td><td><p><strong>x z R F</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UFR to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x R'</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x F R'\">x F R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x F' R'\">x F' R'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>DFR Corner</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UBR to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x F</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x R' F R\">x R' F R</span></p><p>y x U' R' U {UBL}</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"y' x R' F R' F'\">y' x R' F R' F'</span></p><p>y x R U {UBL}</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>UFL to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>x F'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>x U F' U' = x z F R' F'</strong></p><p>x F B F' {DBL}</p></td><td><p><strong>x U' F' U = x z F' R' F</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>DFR to DFR</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x U F U' F'\">x U F U' F'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x↑F' R' F R\">x↑F' R' F R</span></p><p>y' x R U' R2' (DBL open)</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x R' F' R F\">x R' F' R F</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"y' x R F R' F'\">y' x R F R' F'</span></p><p>y' x R2/R' U R' {DBL}</p></td><td><p><strong>SoLved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>LL Corners</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>LL Center</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Side Centers</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Pi</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">L</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x z2 S\">x z2 S</span></p><p>x H</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x S z' S\">x S z' S</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"x S z2' S\">x S z2' S</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S z2' S\">S z2' S</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["F' / f","x z R' F","x F R'","x F' R'","x R' F R","y' x R' F R' F'","x U F U' F'","x↑F' R' F R","x R' F' R F","y' x R F R' F'","x z2 S","x S z' S","x S z2' S","S z2' S"],"thumb":"/stats/data/alg/media/skewb-skewb-lbl/en/image2.svg","warningCount":1,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
